          a single <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">examiner</ENAMEX> reviewed the slides [ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">46 47 51</NUMEX> ] and
          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> stated that experience pathologists reviewed the
          slides [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">45</TIMEX> ] .
          In <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">nine</NUMEX> studies, the biopsy was performed irrespective
