          case-control study [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">44</TIMEX> ] , the control <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> did not
          <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">undergo liver biopsy</ENAMEX>. In <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> studies [ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">38 49</NUMEX> ] , it was
          not clear whether the decision to perform the biopsy was
