          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">51 57</NUMEX> ] . <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Five</NUMEX> studies did not state how many <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">examiners</ENAMEX>
          assessed each <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patient</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</NUMEX> studies reported that a
